General.Name: ABx Group Ltd
General.Description: ABx Group Limited engages in the exploration, development, and production of bauxite resources in Australia. The company develops rare earth element project for bauxite deposit in Queensland. It also develops the Sunrise project, the DL130 bauxite project, and the Penrose projects. The company was formerly known as Australian Bauxite Limited and changed its name to ABx Group Limited in December 2021. ABx Group Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
